<i>- Reset.</i>

160
00:06:20,088 --> 00:06:22,591
As in "reset everything."

161
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,052
HODONG'S BOOKSHOP

162
00:06:25,636 --> 00:06:26,637
LEE JA-RAM'S FAVORITE BOOK

163
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,721
<i>TAKE MY VOICE</i> BY CHUNG SE-RANG

164
00:06:27,804 --> 00:06:31,391
CHUNG'S FIRST SCI-FI COLLECTION THAT
OFFERS CRITIQUES AND HOPE FOR HUMANITY

165
00:06:31,475 --> 00:06:33,477
Chung Se-rang is a famous author.

166
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:36,563
