170
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:44,613
- I see.
- Yes. She contacted me multiple times,

171
00:06:44,696 --> 00:06:46,323
- or so I heard.
- Is that so?

172
00:06:47,574 --> 00:06:48,992
You should watch out.

173
00:06:49,076 --> 00:06:50,661
