at all times.

175
00:06:52,955 --> 00:06:54,164
- I see.
- Yes.

176
00:06:54,248 --> 00:06:56,083
So, what's the story about?

177
00:06:56,166 --> 00:06:57,417
<i>Reset</i>

178
00:06:58,001 --> 00:07:00,504
is a story about the world
literally being reset.

179
00:07:00,587 --> 00:07:02,172
And here's how it's reset.

180
00:07:02,256 --> 00:07:04,216
Giant worms ranging

181
00:07:04,299 --> 00:07:06,301
<i>from 80 to 200 meters in size</i>

182
00:07:06,385 --> 00:07:07,678
<i>fall onto Earth.</i>

183
00:07:07,761 --> 00:07:09,930
<i>And they start eating everything.</i>

184
00:07:10,013 --> 00:07:12,808
<i>Everything that caused damage</i>
<i>to the environment,</i>

185
00:07:12,891 --> 00:07:14,184
<i>and also to humans.</i>

186
00:07:15,102 --> 00:07:16,895
So, humanity

187
00:07:17,437 --> 00:07:20,482
is completely reset.

188
00:07:22,067 --> 00:07:24,403
The plot of the story

189
00:07:24,486 --> 00:07:26,238
sounds horrible and gross.

190
00:07:26,321 --> 00:07:28,824
- I suppose.
- That's why I'm wondering

191
00:07:28,907 --> 00:07:31,493
why this became your favorite.

192
00:07:32,035 --> 00:07:35,831
It reset my thoughts
and made me look at things in a new light.

193
00:07:36,456 --> 00:07:39,835
The idea of a small creature
like a worm becoming so huge

194
00:07:39,918 --> 00:07:42,171
and devouring all of humanity,

195
00:07:42,254 --> 00:07:45,174
which results in a world

196
00:07:45,257 --> 00:07:47,467
where no species is
discriminated against...

197
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:49,761
That shift in perspective made me think,

198
00:07:49,845 --> 00:07:52,139
"Oh, that's right.

199
00:07:52,347 --> 00:07:55,642
I've been assigning a rank
to so many things without realizing it."

200
00:07:55,726 --> 00:07:58,020
My discriminatory perspective

201
00:07:58,395 --> 00:08:01,648
was purified and reset after reading it.

202
00:08:01,732 --> 00:08:06,778
I'd say it broadened my view of the world.

203
00:08:06,862 --> 00:08:09,781
Today, you brought <i>Take My Voice</i> to sell.

204
00:08:09,865 --> 00:08:12,534
